'''Angela Aquereburu''' (wavutse ku ya 11 Mutarama 1977) ni umwanditsi wa sinema, atunganya amafilime akaba n'umuyobozi wa firime.

== Ubuzima ==
Aquereburu yavukiye muri [[Togo]] umubyeyi ukomoka muri [[Gwadelupe|Guadeloupe]] . Ashishikajwe n'ubuhanzi kuva akiri muto, yize muri Togo na Pointe-a-Pitre, Guadeloupe mbere yo kwimukira i Paris kwiga mu ishuri ry'ubucuruzi rya ESCP . <ref name="JA2018" /> Yabonye impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga mu kwihangira imirimo.  Aquereburu yashakanye n'umukinnyi wa filime Jean-Luc Rabatel kandi akora mu bakozi imyaka myinshi. Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubwo yari mu biruhuko muri Togo, yamenye ko kuri televiziyo hari amakinamico gusa, maze afatanije n’umugabo we bazana igitekerezo cyo gukurikiranya filimi yitwa motorcycle taxis. <ref name="JA2018" /> Umwaka ukurikira, Aquereburu na Rabatel bimukiye i Lomé maze bashinga isosiyete ikora amajwi n'amashusho Yobo Studios.  Igitekerezo cyabo cyo kwerekana tagisi cyashingiweho kuri ''Zem'', mini-serie ya episode 26 yiminota itanu, ifatanije na Canal + Afrique. 

Umushinga we ukurikira wari urukurikirane rugufi  rwa filimi ya ''Palabres'' .  Muri 2017, yatangije ''ibitaro IT'', bikemura ibibazo byabaturage nka malariya no kwera uruhu kandi byibanda ku mico Idriss na Tania. Aquereburu yavuze ko yatewe inkunga n'inda ye ya kabiri yo gukora iki gitaramo. Grey's Anatomy yagize uruhare runini.  Yatsindiye igihembo cy'uruhererekane rwiza mu iserukiramuco rya Vues d'Afrique i Montreal. <ref name="Forbes2017" />

